{"home":{"description":"Hi! I'm a freelance director of photography and colourist, currently based in Aberdeen, Scotland, and working throughout Scotland and the UK.\n\nI grew up in the French countryside until I moved to Scotland, aged 18: since then, I've spent years building and improving my filmmaking skillset, and have been involved in many different types of projects, including short films, web series, music videos, or corporate videos. Currently, I also work as camera operator/editor at [Signal](https://signalfilm.tv/), an award-winning Scottish production company.\n\nWith a focus on cinematography and colour grading, I am also a proficient video editor, graphic designer, VFX artist, and even software developer. This perhaps reveals what I enjoy most about content creation: mastering a wide array of technical skills to best articulate a creative idea.","metadescription":"Director of photography and colourist currently based in Aberdeen, Scotland, and working throughout Scotland and the UK on a wide variety of projects, including short films, web series, music videos, or corporate videos.","metaimage":{"url":"/uploads/home_screenshot_505bc01c6d.jpg"},"subtitle":"Cinematography • Colour grading • Software development","underconstruction":false,"images":[{"document":{"tags":[{"name":"Director of Photography / Colourist","icon":"<svg version=\"1.1\" id=\"Layer_1\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" xmlns:xlink=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink\" x=\"0px\" y=\"0px\" \t viewBox=\"0 0 11.5 13.5\" style=\"enable-background:new 0 0 11.5 13.5;\" xml:space=\"preserve\"> <path d=\"M11.5,9.5v-5L9,3.1V2.9l2-2L10.5,0L9,1.5l-2,2H0V10h3v3h1v-3h3l2,2l1.5,1.5l0.5-0.9l-2-2v0L11.5,9.5z M10.5,5.1v3.8L9,9.5 \tV4.2L10.5,5.1z M4,9V7.9c0.6-0.2,1-0.8,1-1.4C5,5.7,4.3,5,3.5,5S2,5.7,2,6.5c0,0.7,0.4,1.2,1,1.4V9H1V4.5h5V9H4z M3,6.5 \tC3,6.2,3.2,6,3.5,6S4,6.2,4,6.5S3.8,7,3.5,7S3,6.8,3,6.5z M7,8.6V4.9l1-1v5.7L7,8.6z\"/> </svg>"}]},"image":{"url":"/uploads/building_after_2_120_2_2d8041b1ba.jpg"